Package: spliceloss
Title: Splice Loss Prediction Using GLMM
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Zhe", "Zhang", , "skymanbp@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Predicting optical fiber splice power losses based on geometric
    features using Generalized Linear Mixed Models (GLMM). This package provides
    tools for data preprocessing, model building, comparison, diagnostics, and
    prediction for fiber optic splice loss analysis.
